title: My Favorite Murder Presents: The Fall Line Season 5 - Episode 1
description:
My Favorite Murder present the first episode of The Fall Line's new season 5 investigating the disappearance of Shy'Kemmia Pate, who vanished from her hometown of Unadilla, Georgia.

Listen and subscribe to The Fall Line on Apple Podcasts, Stitcher, Spotify, or wherever you listen to podcasts.
author: exactlyrightmedia@gmail.com (Exactly Right)
